import React from 'react'
import ReactDom from 'react-dom'
import Uppericons from './uppericons'
import Lowericons from './lowericons'
const MainLayout = () => {
    return (


        <div className = "main-layout" >
        <
        br / >
        <
        div class = "row" >
        <
        div class = "col-sm-2" >
        <
        Uppericons / >
        <
        /div>

        <
        div class = "col-sm-8" >


        <
        div class = "row" >
        <
        div class = "col-sm-12" >
        <
        img src = {
            require('../icons/xunbao text.png')
        }
        className = "xunbaoIcon" / >
        <
        /div> <
        /div>           <
        div class = "row" >
        <
        div class = "col-sm-12" >
        <
        img src = {
            require('../icons/underline.png')
        }
        className = "underlineIcon" / >
        <
        /div> <
        /div>  <
        div class = "row" >
        <
        div class = "col-sm-12" >
        <
        img src = {
            require('../icons/on_li_tr_hnt.png')
        }
        className = "xunbaoText" / >
        <
        /div> <
        /div>  <
        div class = "row" >
        <
        div class = "col-sm-12" >
        <
        img src = {
            require('../icons/play gold.png')
        }
        className = "startButton" / >
        <
        /div> <
        /div>     <
        /div> <
        div class = "col-sm-2" >
        <
        Lowericons / >
        <
        /div>

        <
        /div>



        <
        /div>


    );
}

export default MainLayout;
